  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to uhttpmock</title>

    <para>
      <application>uhttpmock</application> is a HTTP web service mocking project for projects which use libsoup.
      It is used by applications like libgdata for unit testing.  This project is still in its infancy.
    </para>

    &lfs75_checked;

